# Project page; http://www.semicomplete.com/projects/keynav

clear
daemonize

w windowzoom
c cursorzoom 200 200

super+apostrophe start, grid 2x2
Escape end
h cut-left
j cut-down
k cut-up
l cut-right
y cut-left,cut-up
u cut-right,cut-up
n cut-left,cut-down
m cut-right,cut-down

#7 cell-select 1x1
#8 cell-select 2x1
#9 cell-select 3x1
#y cell-select 1x2
#i cell-select 2x2
#o cell-select 3x2
#j cell-select 1x2
#l cell-select 2x2
#k cell-select 3x2

super+h move-left .5
super+j move-down .5
super+k move-up .5
super+l move-right .5
super+y move-left,move-up
super+u move-right,move-up
super+b move-left,move-down
super+n move-right,move-down

apostrophe warp
space warp,click 1
super+space warp,click 3
Return warp,drag 1
super+Return warp,drag 3
1 click 1
2 click 2
3 click 3

